title: Week 12 NFL Recap, Analysis; 49ers Make Statement, Jerry Jones Unhappy (Football 11/25)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 12 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 12 games on the Sunday slate including Packers-49ers, Cowboys-Patriots, Seahawks-Eagles, Panthers-Saints, Dolphins-Browns, Steelers-Bengals, Raiders-Jets, Jags-Titans, Broncos-Bills, Giants-Bears, Bucs-Falcons and Lions-Redskins.
